&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-8550&quot; title=&quot;ActiveMQSslConnectionFactory: Check for null SSL Keystore and Truststore password&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;AMQ-8550&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;AMQ-8550&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; - Check for null keystore/truststore passwords&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Inside ActiveMQSslConnectionFactory the passwords should be checked for&lt;br/&gt;
null so a NPE isn&apos;t thrown. Null will be passed to the factories instead&lt;br/&gt;
and the keystore/truststore factories will try and load the keystores&lt;br/&gt;
using null for the password which may or may not work depending on the&lt;br/&gt;
implementation and if password is set.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(cherry picked from commit b93d58259c86d5e1141d1004cf8d75cf4a4376a6)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
